Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.95,0:01:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從北美出發的卡烏編隊協同夏亞大佐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.10,0:01:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對地球聯邦軍本部賈布羅發動了奇襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.41,0:01:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但因GUNDAM的活躍以及聯邦軍的奮戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.05,0:01:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快便被擊退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.17,0:01:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個夏亞會就這樣放棄麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.80,0:02:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,『小小的防衛線』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.03,0:02:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏是B3地點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.79,0:02:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直至現在一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.23,0:02:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對敵軍的例行探測如常進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.03,0:02:32.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.77,0:02:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這偏辟的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.90,0:02:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍然要作這樣沉悶的報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.77,0:02:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再囉唆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.59,0:02:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰叫你當軍呢！受人錢財當然要這樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.96,0:02:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.62,0:02:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.65,0:03:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是例行轟炸，沒事的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們不用擔心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.82,0:03:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我告訴你們有關於母艦的編制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和現在一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們所屬是帝姆艦隊裏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.11,0:03:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十三獨立部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.03,0:03:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著是宣讀各位的官階
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.90,0:03:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特升中尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.54,0:03:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.39,0:03:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米萊升少尉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.82,0:03:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.54,0:03:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉升軍曹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.83,0:03:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.37,0:03:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們竟在無意間成為正式的軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.41,0:03:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅升曹長！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.97,0:03:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.94,0:03:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱升中仕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.35,0:03:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.55,0:03:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准人升中仕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.94,0:03:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.25,0:04:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了小學畢業拿到證書以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.46,0:04:03.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直至現在才是初次...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這到底有什麼用？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波一等兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.60,0:04:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙勞·波一等兵！聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.13,0:04:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.27,0:04:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.37,0:04:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不去，哪裏也不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.64,0:04:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.17,0:04:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.95,0:04:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底甚麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.32,0:04:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，他們三個不肯到育幼中心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.82,0:04:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎可胡來的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我來吧，這種事我是專家呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待我來勸勸他們吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.83,0:04:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了，妳可以一起來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.30,0:04:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳先接受了軍令再說吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.83,0:04:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有良為軍隊奮勇作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.00,0:04:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不幸殉職，特此進升兩級
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.64,0:04:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被任命為中尉官階
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.64,0:04:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有其它殉職的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.66,0:04:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一律可進升兩級，散會！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.01,0:04:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特別進升兩級？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.51,0:05:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是進升兩級而已...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.33,0:05:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進升兩級，就只有這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.87,0:05:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,進升兩級，只有這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就只有這點，到底有什麼用啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.94,0:05:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼？你這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在作戰時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.36,0:05:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們卻一點也不加以支持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.68,0:05:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是用一張證明書對那班殉職的人這樣就想算數？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了吧，阿姆囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你究竟想怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.99,0:05:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理，竟然閃避？你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果再閃避，我就要你關進入牢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.70,0:05:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是因為你太多口之故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.97,0:05:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶然被人教訓一下也有好處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.10,0:05:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白了，別再提吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小琪他們現在怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.51,0:06:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那軍官說那裏有很多好玩的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.01,0:06:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，他們終於答應去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.68,0:06:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過...他們三個在那裏生活會覺得幸福嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸福？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.61,0:06:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想他們到那裏也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.32,0:06:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的是這樣想嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在當然是留他們在育兒中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.13,0:06:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是最好的辦法呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.14,0:06:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼小的孩子看著大人們互相殘殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會是好事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.94,0:06:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也說得對！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.87,0:07:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞上校，我們已經準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我們去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.35,0:07:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果汁！果汁！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.82,0:07:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好美味的果汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要大杯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過做無聊的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為小孩子天真不好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.46,0:07:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因你們這樣只是令大人開心而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.27,0:07:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看來才不可愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你一直在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.30,0:07:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後也會和我一樣的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.28,0:07:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是戰爭期中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.37,0:07:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,？？？？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.95,0:07:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在這裏只有一直等爸爸媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來看看我一面而已...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.05,0:07:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽...爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再說了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.29,0:07:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,豈有此理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.36,0:08:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姐姐啊！我要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.84,0:08:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，弄成她那樣子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.84,0:08:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不也是...很想回家去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.32,0:08:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她來了，快走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.42,0:08:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走啊，小琪，我們走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.65,0:08:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別走啊，卡茲、列茲、吉卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們去那裏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.94,0:08:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快回來，你們聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.01,0:08:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應一應我吧！卡茲、列茲、吉卡！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唔，有人來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下，好像是小孩呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.84,0:09:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧，小琪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.51,0:09:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心，很滑的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝仔，快點！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像走了呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.80,0:09:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.89,0:09:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到聯邦軍頗先進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏的只是一小部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.81,0:09:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始嗎？上校？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.18,0:09:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賴忠你留在這裏！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和赤鼻部隊就去木馬艙那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.45,0:10:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就最好呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊，在這裏被抓到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又會被送回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不行了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.47,0:10:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小琪，振作起來吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒你辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.98,0:10:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，原來門沒上鎖的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.98,0:10:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.98,0:10:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小琪，我們就在此休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.23,0:10:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後再回母艦好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.24,0:10:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有多久？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.58,0:10:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5分鐘可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等，有三人入來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.35,0:10:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很黑暗呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，有很多GUNDAM呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.05,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢，很利害啊！真的很多呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但...看下來好像有點不同！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說又好像是呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.47,0:10:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...那邊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.74,0:10:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.44,0:10:56.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那...那裏有東西動呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.37,0:10:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.15,0:11:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是妳看錯了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過...明明是有的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的，腳下邊真的有東西在動！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,？？？？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.62,0:11:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道是ZION軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那快通知大家吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很瞭解妳的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們現在一定在哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在只想再見他們一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.83,0:11:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怕是偷偷地多看一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.90,0:11:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀！那個不是保母軍官？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在這裏就好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.91,0:11:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小琪他們逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.24,0:11:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們千萬別怪我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.41,0:11:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已較好計時炸彈30分鐘後爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.81,0:11:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.60,0:12:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸彈啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.77,0:12:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們等了很久嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.57,0:12:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,許可證的領取手續很麻煩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.23,0:12:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就好了，終於可以外出參觀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱，你去不去呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.30,0:12:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去看看吉姆工場也好吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀...外出散散悶也好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.38,0:12:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布萊特中尉，立刻到會議室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.91,0:12:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有重要事商量！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.34,0:12:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一當了軍人就要這樣的了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.58,0:12:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們自己去參觀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.75,0:12:51.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你們會這樣高興的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.66,0:13:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝仔，快四處看將炸彈拆下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.47,0:13:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝仔，小琪快下去看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.47,0:13:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.13,0:13:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.44,0:13:18.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，再下去這裏會爆炸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.01,0:13:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了！怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.28,0:13:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是不是炸彈呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.65,0:13:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏也有...還有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.78,0:13:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小琪，快些啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.59,0:14:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡，快開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.27,0:14:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快開啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.06,0:14:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快些啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想快，但怎樣也開不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底，你懂不懂開動的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.97,0:14:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我有辦法啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.18,0:14:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了，可以開動了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.48,0:14:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，下一步是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.96,0:14:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照看可以了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.28,0:14:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很難控制！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.96,0:14:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是勝仔他們呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.33,0:14:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何會在這地方出現的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.63,0:14:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們追上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快將車停下來，勝仔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.65,0:14:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快停下來！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.35,0:14:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.98,0:14:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.85,0:14:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION軍將炸彈裝在工場內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.85,0:15:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們把它拿走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.05,0:15:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸彈？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.37,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.70,0:15:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.52,0:15:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來是計時炸彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.99,0:15:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那個工場找到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.66,0:15:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在GUNDAM工場內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.33,0:15:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏等我處理吧！你們乘准人的那輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.14,0:15:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.33,0:15:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凱，請你將他們接過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.37,0:15:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你即管放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，亞發，你先過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.03,0:15:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓緊我不用怕的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.04,0:15:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1，2，3！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.21,0:15:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.94,0:15:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次輪到你了，小琪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.56,0:15:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝仔，到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.31,0:15:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有問題吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.17,0:15:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿姆羅，得了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.39,0:15:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你了，凱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.22,0:16:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,White Base有危險啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看裝炸彈的ZION軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.46,0:16:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕連母艦也不會放過的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.37,0:16:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,賴忠那邊似乎成功了呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.07,0:16:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞勇，你聽到嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，夏亞上校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.41,0:16:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這裏失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快用MS引開他們的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.95,0:16:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.30,0:17:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於開戰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.51,0:17:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎有MS呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.96,0:17:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小琪，勝仔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,？？？？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝仔，小琪，亞發...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.23,0:17:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿爾黛西亞...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.42,0:17:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會的，如果你是我哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定不會是ZION軍的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你聽我說離開軍隊吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿爾黛西亞妹妹！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.25,0:18:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，妳在那裏？答我吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.30,0:18:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開軍隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.24,0:18:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.87,0:18:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.85,0:18:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在那裏，阿勝...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.59,0:18:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才槍聲是什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有ZION軍嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說ZION軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.01,0:18:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道妳不見那人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明看到的啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.79,0:18:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起，看來去那邊較安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.95,0:18:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞上校！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別理了，撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.86,0:18:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要作戰失敗就立即撤退，知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.89,0:18:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.29,0:19:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出發！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今次我是不會放過你們的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞上校...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.92,0:19:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上校，亞楊的MS被毀了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.03,0:19:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.16,0:19:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰停下來便會沒命的，快走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.81,0:19:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.62,0:20:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會給你們走的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.09,0:20:06.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他又來了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.54,0:20:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的MS一下子就給他毀滅了兩台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不認輸也不行了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.95,0:20:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有地上水路！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.79,0:20:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然使用這一招！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.14,0:20:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏亞真狡滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.47,0:21:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又被他逃走了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很瞭解你們的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.83,0:21:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他們留在這裏會比較安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.83,0:21:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而他們將來也成為聯邦軍的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以一定要小心照顧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果又有今日的情況又怎辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.44,0:21:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，一想到他們的感受...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.65,0:21:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.99,0:21:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳說他們是聯邦軍的末來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.78,0:21:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我認為他們長大後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.68,0:21:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZION和聯邦的戰爭也結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.26,0:21:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,？？？？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.27,0:21:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這三個小孩和一般的不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.38,0:21:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他們已經過一次又一次的冒險激烈的炮火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.93,0:21:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我們一起奮戰對抗敵軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.90,0:22:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們已像大人般經歷戰爭場面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.95,0:22:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以他們的年齡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.60,0:22:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以經過這麼多的世情
